==English==
===Etymology===
'''Gulf''' (the [[Gulf of Mexico]]) + '''[[stream]]'''.
===Noun===
'''Gulf Stream'''
# A warm [[ocean current]] flowing issuing from the [[Gulf of Mexico]], flowing [[northeastwards]] along the coast of [[North America]] to the [[Grand Banks]] where it breaks eastwards across the [[Atlantic Ocean]]. A branch of the current maintains warm temperatures along the west coasts of the [[British Isles]].

